SHADOW MATE
===========

Ingredients
-----------

1.5 lb Turbinado sugar
1 tsp guarana powder
1/2 cup lemon juice
1/2 cup lime juice
1/2 lb Yerba Mate 
2 oz Siberian ginseng (rough cut, not powdered)
5 Gallons water

Process
-------

Bring water to a boil. Add guarana, sugar, lemon, and lime. Sustain
boil for 3 minutes. Remove heat, add ginseng and Mate. Let steep Â½
hour. Move to keg when cool enough to pour, filter while pouring. Cool
and carbonate to 15 psi.